/*
 * SPDX-License-Identifier: MIT
 *
 * Wiring contract preserved from the Arduino quicksetup:
 * - MR60BHA2 UART RX: GPIO17
 * - MR60BHA2 UART TX: GPIO16
 * - WS2812 RGB LED: GPIO1
 * - BH1750 I2C SDA: GPIO22
 * - BH1750 I2C SCL: GPIO23
 *
 * The first Zephyr milestone uses USB serial JSON output only. Pin mux and
 * peripheral aliases should be enabled here during the hardware bring-up pass
 * after the board target is confirmed in the local Zephyr checkout.
 */
